{"tid":2371430,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"貼錢打工就破產","createTime":"2021-01-19T00:37:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T02:28:19.000Z","uid":383204,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"90b080fc5acc56013c3f408166f1b01ad1876605","tid":2371430,"uid":383204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T00:37:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210119/IRVVEP73VFA3JEVA6UCGFIYEB4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210119%2FIRVVEP73VFA3JEVA6UCGFIYEB4%2F&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrHXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=da4dbb44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210119%2FIRVVEP73VFA3JEVA6UCGFIYEB4%2F&h=3087601e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210119/IRVVEP73VFA3JEVA6UCGFIYEB4/</a><br />\n<br />\n//由中學開始接觸議員助理工作，李志宏自言是窮人一個，當年每月薪金3,000、之後也不過數千元。今年25歲，笑言人生戶口「未試過有多過10萬」，當選後再要承擔議辦開支，窮上加窮。面對要預付的金錢越來越多，去年10月李志宏只好向銀行借錢，又因為沒有物業，只可選擇一般貸款，「惟有畀貴啲息囉！」記者訪問當日和李志宏到櫃員機提款，問銀行借回來的20萬元亦已用盡，戶口僅餘1,171.33元。//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"549cbbdd90011d4db886524b0708bc54a7d2c710","tid":2371430,"uid":298796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:27:33.000Z","msg":"無得攪, 公務員拖數批數唔係第一日既事<br />\n佢地既籍口就係上頭未批, 而唔會反應去追去問D未批既野<br />\n咁未比班所謂中層官僚愈黎愈霸道囉<br />\n所以有人話公務話都係巴絲, 你諗你啦"},{"pid":"1d6940c06cc73522bf0ff631d63446bead7a3e04","tid":2371430,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:28:19.000Z","msg":"藍架"}]}